{"tid":1438211,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我地下一步要聽天琦講 做呢樣野","createTime":"2019-08-09T17:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T18:20:35.000Z","uid":22855,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"63a6f77c64ae95da9669b9114249b75768e57336","tid":1438211,"uid":22855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:05:36.000Z","msg":"梁天琦: 不要被仇恨支配自己<br />\n<br />\n「政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，<br />\n<br />\n而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圍內互屌真係冇用，依家應該要鬥同林鄭搶班中立派既目光<br />\n<br />\n我建議可以文宣多D最基本精簡，用字平實既Q an A, 等D 冷感撚重新了解發生咩事，同埋當我地要同人解釋既時候，有論據論證可以copy下， 咁先有最大效用同可持久打落去<br />\n<br />\n同埋可以諗下點樣擴大平民記者會既觀眾群<br />\n<br />\n唔係再咁搞法 只會被政府愈抹愈黑 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當時雨革都係大家互屌 屌到心灰意冷 最後收皮 絕對唔可以比佢重演！！！！"},{"pid":"175006c6e400bf6700c43c6fd55e4f788ce32f0d","tid":1438211,"uid":22855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:06:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a1fad6dd45581f8d241c824796a697f051e0755","tid":1438211,"uid":244133,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:06:18.000Z","msg":"聽日理撚得你去大埔定機場 <br />\n去大埔嘅自己小心 記住<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">be water</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地要睇嘅得呢一句：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">宇宙大爆炸都唔撚割！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6457e0473059a90421180cb27a810c64d293d81c","tid":1438211,"uid":22855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbeb718114daf2dfba01d8f3b2e5dd7f682f018","tid":1438211,"uid":22855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hk